    <detaileddescription>
<para><verbatim>Members:

  ContourOrientation : detect sign of distance based on closest contour&apos;s edge turn\\n
(recommended for good contours with no self-intersections)
\\note that polyline topology should be consistently oriented \\n

  WindingRule : detect sign of distance based on number of ray intersections with contours\\n
(recommended for contours with self-intersections)
</verbatim> </para>
